heroProducts.name: Nike Air Force 1 Mid W
heroProducts.description:
Since it first debuted in 1985, Nike’s Air Force 1 silhouette has been presented in a number of iterations and colourways. Its latest variant is dressed in a white summit and coconut milk colourway, with star shaped cut-outs featuring on the smooth leather uppers for an out-of-this-world touch. The hi-top design is, as usual, supported by a comfy rubber outsole while signature profile Swooshes at the sidewalls round off the design.

  • Leather Uppers
  • Rubber Outsole
  • Style Code: DV3451-100

heroProducts.name: Acronym Panelled Coach Jacket
heroProducts.description:
This SS22, Acronym reimagines an outerwear staple with this black panelled coach jacket. Fitting to a classic straight style, its hard-shell 2L GORE-TEX INFINIUM™ construction promises to fight off harsh winds while you’re on-the-go, while inside, a recycled mesh body lining helps to circulate air and increase ventilation for optimal comfort. Acronyms’ famous FORCELOCK technology allows you to place your earbuds at the neckline – and you’ll find a sling incorporated into the design too so you can wear the jacket on your back when not in use. Secured with a zip and snap-button closure, this hi-tech piece is a must-have for your trans-seasonal collection.

  • 43% Nylon, 57% ePTFE
  • Mesh Body Lining
  • Zip & Snap Button Closure
  • GORE-TEX INFINIUM™ Shell
  • FORCELOCK Technology
  • JacketSling

heroProducts.home_title: REEBOK X MAISON MARGIELA PROJECT 0 THE QUESTION
heroProducts.name: Reebok x Maison Margiela Project 0 The Question
heroProducts.description:
Reebok joins forces with Maison Margiela this season to present this white pair of Question Mids. The duo reshuffles the original shoe’s pattern pieces to uncover its seam allowance and the oval holes are used as eyelets, creating lacing reminiscent of gillies.

Margiela then deconstructs the design – parts of the sneaker’s padded areas have been cut to reveal the inside foam as well as the protective tricot mesh overlay. A debossed number 22 then features on the heel, as a nod to famous basketball player Allen Iverson.

  • Leather Uppers
  • EVA Midsole
  • Rubber Outsole
